Accessing Small LeibnizAlgebra AllSmallLeibnizAlgebra is an accessor function for accessing the complete list of non-isomorphic LeibnizAlgebra of orders 2 to 4.
<#Include Label = "AllSmallLeibnizAlgebra">
The output leibnizalgebra are represented by its operation table for +, f, a, as given in Section .

Checking Models of Small LeibnizAlgebra
"IsASmallLeibnizAlgebra" is a function for checking a model against the complete list of non-isomorphic LeibnizAlgebra of orders 2 to 4. It returns true if the model is a Small LeibnizAlgebra, false otherwise.
